==使用方式==
将以下原始码插入条目页面的最顶端：
<syntaxhighlight lang="html5">
{{Infobox_history
|image = <!-- 建議使用自由版權圖像 -->
|imagestyle =
|caption =
|name =
|english_names =
|foreign_names =
|other_names =
|author =
|date of start = 

|date of end = 
|languages = 
}}
</syntaxhighlight>
